    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the church, we all can apprehend"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All the riches of this life that is within."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not just shallowness with strife,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But a deep and peaceful life"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is just waiting to flow out, a living spring."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With the saints it's easy to be bold,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To pursue this life, to gain it, to lay hold."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All the other things we find,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Must be quickly left behind,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So that only life remains for us to see."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Lord, we're just for Your flowing;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How we need a deeper knowing!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Life is why we're here"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And why You've come in us."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Turn us, Lord, turn us now;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Turn us deeply—Life is how"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You will get the church,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The home You're longing for."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Deeper, Lord our turn must be to You;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We would move by life in everything we do;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All our concepts refute,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For Your life be absolute—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Grant us grace to turn much deeper day by day."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "When we touch our spirit—such a thrill!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This is far beyond emotion, mind, and will—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It's within our hidden part—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come, make home in all our heart;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let Your presence flow as rivers deep within."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
